---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Pocket Door Roller Replacement & Frame Repair | Florida's Pocket Door Experts"
  description="Pocket door stuck or dragging? Expert roller replacement and frame repair across Orlando, Miami & Fort Myers. Weight-matched hardware, no wall damage. Free estimates. Call (954) 727-5410."
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative bg-primary text-white py-6 md:py-8 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center opacity-20" style="background-image: url('/images/new trracks.webp')" role="img" aria-label="Pocket door roller replacement and frame repair service"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/75 to-primary/50"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <h1 class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-7xl tracking-wide mb-4">Pocket Door Roller Replacement & Frame Repair</h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-light mb-4 text-gray-200">The #1 Reason Pocket Doors Fail — And How We Fix It</p>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-300 mb-8">
          Worn rollers are behind most pocket door problems — the door drags, jumps the track, or won't close flush. Instead of forcing it (which bends the track and makes everything worse), call the specialists. We replace rollers with hardware matched to your door's exact weight and realign the frame so it glides like the day it was installed.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 mb-12">
          <a href="tel:9547275410" class="bg-white text-primary font-heading text-xl tracking-wide px-8 py-4 rounded hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors text-center" aria-label="Call Pocket Door Services">
            (954) 727-5410
          </a>
          <a href="/contact" class="border-2 border-white text-white font-heading text-xl tracking-wide px-8 py-4 rounded hover:bg-white hover:text-primary transition-colors text-center">
            FREE ESTIMATE
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl tracking-wide text-primary mb-4">What Actually Goes Wrong Inside the Wall</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Pocket door rollers carry the full weight of the door as it slides in and out of the wall cavity. Over time — especially if the wrong roller grade was installed originally — they wear flat, corrode in Florida's humidity, or crack under the load. The result is a door that sticks, scrapes, wobbles, or derails completely. Not sure if your rollers are the problem? Check our guide on <a href='/blog/signs-your-pocket-door-rollers-need-replacing' class='text-accent hover:underline'>5 signs your pocket door rollers need replacing</a>.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          We start every roller replacement by removing the door from the track and inspecting the entire system: rollers, track condition, frame alignment, and guide hardware. This matters because replacing rollers on a bent track or misaligned frame just creates the same problem again in a few months. Most companies skip this step.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Once we know the full picture, we replace rollers with contractor-grade components rated for your door's weight — not the one-size-fits-all rollers from the hardware store. If the frame needs repair or reinforcement, we handle that too. Every job ends with a smooth-glide test and door adjustment so the door sits flush when closed.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          For commercial properties with high-traffic pocket doors, we recommend heavy-duty roller systems that handle thousands of daily cycles without degrading. We also offer preventive maintenance programs to catch roller wear before it becomes a breakdown. Learn more about our <a href='/service/commercial-door-repair' class='text-accent hover:underline'>commercial door repair services</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <img src="/images/old tracks.webp" alt="Pocket door roller replacement and frame repair in Florida" class="rounded-lg shadow-lg w-full" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Choose Us -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-light">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl text-center tracking-wide text-primary mb-10">Why Choose Pocket Door Services</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        {[
          { name: "Fast & Reliable", icon: "M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" },
          { name: "Transparent Pricing", icon: "M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" },
          { name: "Emergency 24/7", icon: "M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" },
          { name: "Expert Technicians", icon: "M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" },
        ].map((f) => (
          <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-accent rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d={f.icon} /></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg tracking-wide text-primary">{f.name}</h3>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Other Services -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl text-center tracking-wide text-primary mb-10">Our Other Services</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {[
          { name: "Lock Repair", href: "/service/lock-repair", image: "/images/new lock.webp" },
          { name: "Hinge Repair/Replacement", href: "/service/hinge-repair-replacement", image: "/images/pocket door 2.webp" },
          { name: "Commercial Door Installation", href: "/service/commercial-door-installation", image: "/images/client photo.webp" },
          { name: "Commercial Door Repair", href: "/service/commercial-door-repair", image: "/images/walk through.webp" },
          { name: "Commercial Door Lock Services", href: "/service/commercial-door-lock-services", image: "/images/worker.webp" },
        ].map((s) => (
          <a href={s.href} class="group bg-white rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-border/30">
            <div class="aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden">
              <img src={s.image} alt={`${s.name} service`} class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
            <div class="p-5">
              <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl tracking-wide text-primary">{s.name}</h3>
            </div>
          </a>
        ))}
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center bg-primary rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 text-center text-white">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 mb-4 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" /></svg>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl tracking-wide mb-2">Not Sure What You Need?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-4">Tell us what's going on with your door and we'll recommend the right service. Free estimates, no obligation.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex bg-accent text-white font-heading tracking-wide px-6 py-3 rounded hover:bg-blue-600 transition-colors">GET A FREE ESTIMATE</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- From Our Blog -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-light">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl tracking-wide text-primary mb-4">From Our Blog</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Learn more about pocket door roller issues and when to call a professional.</p>
      <a href="/blog/signs-your-pocket-door-rollers-need-replacing" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-all border border-gray-border/30 text-left">
        <img src="/images/old tracks.webp" alt="Worn pocket door rollers" class="w-24 h-24 rounded-lg object-cover flex-shrink-0" />
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl tracking-wide text-primary group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">5 Signs Your Pocket Door Rollers Need Replacing</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-1">March 24, 2026 · 8 min read</p>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-primary text-white text-center">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl tracking-wide mb-4">Pocket Door Dragging or Off Track?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Don't force a struggling pocket door — it causes more damage. Call us for a same-day diagnostic and get your door sliding smoothly again. We serve Orlando, Miami, and Fort Myers with 24/7 emergency availability.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="tel:9547275410" class="inline-flex bg-accent text-white font-heading text-xl tracking-wide px-8 py-4 rounded hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">Call Now (954) 727-5410</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex border-2 border-white text-white font-heading text-xl tracking-wide px-8 py-4 rounded hover:bg-white hover:text-primary transition-colors">FREE ESTIMATE</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
